MISC
====
Connection
----------
*le client se connecte*
server  : `hi id_client`

Roomlist
--------
client  : `ask roomlist`
server  : `rep roomlist start`
server  : `rep roomlist room ROOMSERIALIZATION`
server  : `...`
server  : `rep roomlist room ROOMSERIALIZATION`
server  : `rep roomlist end`

Room details
------------
client  : `ask room_details ID`
client  : `ask room_details ID start`
server  : `rep room_details ID room ROOMSERIALIZATION`
server  : `rep room_details ID player status PLAYERSERIALIZATION`
server  : `rep room_details ID player ...`
server  : `rep room_details ID end`


Interagir avec les room
=======================
- quand on rejoint/creer une partie, le joueur souscrit automatiquement aux 
updates de cette room
- les raisons sont toutes *url encoded*

Join
----
client  : `ask join ID`
server  : `rep join OK ID`
OU
server  : `rep join KO ID reason` 


Create
------
client  : `ask create`
server  : `rep create OK ID`
OU
server  : `rep create KO reason`

Leave
-----
client  : `ask leave ID`
server  : `rep leave OK`
OU
server  : `rep leave KO reason`

Notifications
=============

Joueur
------
server  : `notif player join ROOM_ID PLAYERSERIALIZATION`
server  : `notif player ready ROOM_ID PLAYERSERIALIZATION`
server  : `notif player not_ready ROOM_ID PLAYERSERIALIZATION`
server  : `notif player leave ROOM_ID PLAYERSERIALIZATION`

Partie
------
server  : `notif gamestart ROOM_ID`
server  : `notif gameend ROOM_ID distance_parcouru`

Serialisation
=============

Joueur
------
`id ip login`

Room
----
`id status playercount playermax maxdistance`
